snippet.title: EverQuest 2: Terrors of Thalumbra [Official Trailer]
snippet.description:
Terrors of Thalumbra is now available! BUY NOW: https://bit.ly/EQ2-ToT

Deep underneath Norrath lies a realm on the edge of the Plane of the Underfoot, known as Thalumbra. This expansive, subterranean domain is home to fabled races and ancient terrors! Terrors of Thalumbra is the 12th EverQuest II expansion and brings new adventures to Norrath.

Did you know you can play EverQuest II for FREE? https://www.everquest2.com/register
